WEBVTT

00:00:00.597 --> 00:00:02.478
When you're a child,

00:00:02.478 --> 00:00:06.077
anything and everything is possible.

00:00:06.147 --> 00:00:10.186
The challenge, so often,
is hanging on to that as we grow up.

00:00:10.596 --> 00:00:12.181
And as a four-year-old,

00:00:12.181 --> 00:00:14.841
I had the opportunity
to sail for the first time.

00:00:15.671 --> 00:00:19.878
I will never forget
the excitement as we closed the coast.

00:00:19.878 --> 00:00:21.643
I will never forget

00:00:21.643 --> 00:00:24.638
the feeling of adventure
as I climbed on board the boat

00:00:24.638 --> 00:00:28.280
and stared into her tiny cabin
for the first time.

00:00:28.280 --> 00:00:31.488
But the most amazing feeling
was the feeling of freedom,